<% const startLabel = winLogo + ' ' + startText; %>
    <section class="component">
      <h3 id="taskbar">Taskbar</h3>
      <div>
        <p>What would Windows be without the Taskbar and Start Button?</p>

        <p>All the parts for the taskbar, including the Start Button and Notification tray, are handled using three classes: <code>start-button</code>, <code>open-applications</code> and <code>notification-tray</code>.</p>

        <p>We make use of <code>aria-label</code> to render the (functioning) tray expand button. </p>

        <p>Taskbar buttons (<code>app-button</code> class) go into the <code>running-applications</code> element. The tabs will resize if there are too many to fit in the space. The <code>active</code> class is for <a href="#inactive-windows">active/inactive windows</a></p>

        <h4>Start Button</h4>
        <p>The Start Button is a molecule that hugs its content — only its width changes based on the label. This makes it suitable for localisation where the label text may vary in length.</p>

        <p>The button has three visual states: default, hover, and active (pressed).</p>

        <%- example(`
        <div class="taskbar" style="width: fit-content; overflow: visible;">
          <div class="start-button" aria-label="start-button">
            <label>${startLabel}</label>
          </div>
          <div class="start-button hover" aria-label="start-button">
            <label>${startLabel}</label>
          </div>
          <div class="start-button active" aria-label="start-button">
            <label>${startLabel}</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        `) %>

        <h4>Full Taskbar</h4>

        <%- example(`
        <div class="desktop" style="width: 900px;">
          <div class="taskbar">
            <div class="start-button" aria-label="start-button">
              <label id="start">
                <input type="checkbox" name="start" id="startcheck">
                ${startLabel}
              </label>
            </div>
            <div class="running-applications">
              <div class="app-button active">
                <img src="https://img.icons8.com/office/16/command-line.png" aria-label="from icons8.com">
                <span> Command Prompt</span>
              </div>
              <div class="app-button">
                <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/16/internet-explorer.png" aria-label="from icons8.com">
                <span> how to center a div - Google Search</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="notification-tray">
              <div class="external"></div>
              <div class="internal">
                <div class="icon-container">
                  <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color-glass/18/github--v1.png" aria-info="from icons8.com"/>
                </div>
                <div class="clock">12:12 AM</div>
              </div>
              <label aria-label="notif-expand"><input type="checkbox" name="notif-expand"></label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        `) %>
      </div>
    </section>
